I.u[11222] = {n:"Pingwinkle Beak",t:47,d:"When it\'s not planted firmly in the jaw of the Pingwinkle, this beak can be found planted firmly in your backside.",ep:0,g:662,l:115,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11223] = {n:"Pingwinkle Feather",t:53,d:"In olden times, Pingwinkles only used to visit Frigost\'s shores for a few days during the winter, but now the island has frozen over completely, they\'ve decided to stay - which is as good an excuse as any to steal their feathers all year round.",ep:0,g:646,l:115,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11224] = {n:"Pingwobble Wing",t:104,d:"Frigostians have often wondered what purpose these ridiculous wings could serve. After all, a Pingwobble could never possibly hope to take off.",ep:0,g:216,l:120,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11225] = {n:"Pingwobble Skin",t:59,d:"It\'s very oily, isn\'t washed very often, and it shines. Nope, I\'m not talking about your wig, but this Pingwobble Skin.",ep:0,g:49,l:120,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11226] = {n:"Mama Pingwin Oil",t:60,d:"This oil was extracted from a Mama Pingwin. It will take you a very long time to wipe the memory of how exactly you extracted it from your scarred mind.",ep:0,g:72,l:125,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11227] = {n:"Mama Pingwin Down",t:54,d:"Everyone on Frigost loves to stuff their underwear with Mama Pingwin down. Some people say they do it to keep warm, but only a Iop would believe that.",ep:0,g:675,l:125,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11228] = {n:"Shaman Pingwin Giant Fishbone",t:47,d:"There are plenty of questions about Frigost that don\'t have answers, and, more worryingly, plenty of answers that don\'t have questions. You will never know where the Shaman Pingwin found this giant fishbone.",ep:0,g:663,l:130,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11229] = {n:"Shaman Pingwin Beard Hair",t:54,d:"The Shaman Pingwin\'s Beard smells of fish and goat musk.  This potent mix is used by the bravest inhabitants of Frigost as a Mastogob repellent.",ep:0,g:674,l:130,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11230] = {n:"Kung-Fu Pingwin Tail",t:65,d:"Don\'t be fooled by its modest size, it knows exactly where it\'s going.",ep:0,g:753,l:135,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11231] = {n:"Kung-Fu Pingwin Ear",t:106,d:"Usually hidden by a decaying fish, the ears of the Kung-Fu Pingwin hear one thing, the calls of available partners during mating season. So you\'re free to make fun of Kung-Fu Pingwins in perfectly safety as long as you don\'t look like a potential partner.",ep:0,g:625,l:135,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11232] = {n:"Royal Pingwin Feather",t:53,d:"The Royal Pingwin is well respected by the inhabitants of Frigost, who, blinded by his noble title, think he\'s probably more important than he actually is, and don\'t hesitate to kill him as a result.",ep:0,g:647,l:145,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11233] = {n:"Royal Pingwin Egg",t:105,d:"Don\'t pretend you don\'t know exactly which hole this enormous egg came out of.",ep:0,g:643,l:135,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11234] = {n:"Red Richard",t:32,d:"This survivor from the Lonesome Pine Trails should be escorted to Chief Anbifketf.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:false,w:0,an:0,m:true,p:1};
I.u[11235] = {n:"Sioux Stuarme",t:32,d:"This survivor from the Lonesome Pine Trails should be escorted to Chief Anbifketf.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:false,w:0,an:0,m:true,p:1};
I.u[11236] = {n:"Jauni Staurme",t:32,d:"This survivor from the Lonesome Pine Trails should be escorted to Chief Anbifketf.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:false,w:0,an:0,m:true,p:1};
I.u[11237] = {n:"Grimmben",t:32,d:"This survivor from the Lonesome Pine Trails should be escorted to Chief Anbifketf.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:false,w:0,an:0,m:true,p:1};
I.u[11238] = {n:"Skrat Tail",t:65,d:"Skrats use their tails to balance when they\'re rolling their acorns along the floor. Skrats seem impervious to ridicule.",ep:0,g:754,l:115,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11239] = {n:"Skrat Acorn",t:58,d:"Skrats spend the first few years of their lives looking for the best acorn possible. They spend the rest of their lives trying to remember why they\'ve hidden it.",ep:0,g:68,l:115,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11240] = {n:"Sabredon Tooth",t:47,d:"A very serious, progressive scientific study has shown that the teeth of the Sabredon were the very first cause of perforated buttock amongst the Frigostian population.",ep:0,g:664,l:120,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11241] = {n:"Sabredon Hair",t:54,d:"Sabredon Hairs were once used to stuff quilts - which certain Frigostians of dubious personal hygiene could then use as an excuse to mask their polecat stench.",ep:0,g:676,l:120,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11242] = {n:"Glacial Boar Tusk",t:47,d:"This tusk smells like someone\'s underpants. Not yours, though.",ep:0,g:665,l:125,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11243] = {n:"Glacial Boar Leather",t:56,d:"A Glacial Boar\'s skin pads its angular bones quite nicely, meaning it stays festively plump all year round.",ep:0,g:16,l:125,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11244] = {n:"Gerard\'s Message",t:24,d:"I followed a hoary Mama Pingwin and she led me to her den, where hundreds of other Mama Pingwins were hiding. It\'s an opportunity  not to be missed. I\'m going to head inside and shoot anything that moves, there\'ll be enough meat for the next decade.\nGerard.",ep:0,g:176,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11245] = {n:"Gerard\'s Family Jewels",t:24,d:"Unlike those of the Moowolf, these family jewels have neither value nor purpose.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11246] = {n:"Frighog Baleful Eye",t:109,d:"Just before shuffling off this mortal coil and joining the sanctuary of Frighogs killed in action, the one you killed gave you a last look of such ferocity that your blood ran cold. As if it wasn\'t cold enough already on Frigost...",ep:0,g:591,l:130,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11247] = {n:"Frighog Pierced Ear",t:106,d:"A Frighog\'s ears are pierced all over. Is this because they like piercings, or is it because you can even hear Jon Lemon\'s songs on Frigost too?",ep:0,g:626,l:130,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11248] = {n:"Kanigloo Ear",t:106,d:"This ear reminds you of one of the favourite songs of young Frigostians: \"Kanigloo gloo gloo, Greedoblop blop blop tadada tzum tzum\". There aren\'t many lyrics, sure, but that way a Iop can just about memorise it.",ep:0,g:627,l:135,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11249] = {n:"Kanigloo Fabric",t:55,d:"This fabric reminds you of the second verse of one of the favourite songs of young Frigostians: \"Frighog hog hog...\". Unfortunately, you don\'t remember the rest of the words.",ep:0,g:730,l:135,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11250] = {n:"Woolly Bow Meow Hair",t:54,d:"While they were still alive, the Mayor of Frigost\'s political opponents would tell anyone who would listen that she wore Wooly Bow Meow Hair lingerie.",ep:0,g:677,l:85,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11251] = {n:"Woolly Bow Meow Sternum",t:47,d:"No one knows for certain what exactly this sternum is used for.",ep:0,g:666,l:85,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11252] = {n:"Stunted Rat Paw",t:103,d:"Young Frigostian schoolchildren have a game called \"BowMeouch\" which involves cutting a paw off a Stunted Rat and using it to simulate footprints in the snow. They attract Snow Bow Meows in search of prey to ambush. Once the Snow Bow Meow is caught, they shave its fur off and turn it into a muffle. Aren\'t children wonderful?",ep:0,g:36,l:95,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11253] = {n:"Stunted Rat Fabric",t:55,d:"Before Frigost froze over, Stunted Rats were hunted for their fur, which was then sold on the Amaknean continent under the name \"Exotic Kitsou Skin\".",ep:0,g:731,l:95,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11254] = {n:"Crabeye Pincer",t:47,d:"Crabeyes are hunted by the fishermen of Frigost for two reasons: their permanent bad temper and their tendency to play jokes on the fishermen by snipping their nets with their pincers. The fishermen get their revenge, and play jokes on the crabs by snipping their pincers off.",ep:0,g:668,l:65,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11255] = {n:"Crabeye Eye",t:109,d:"The eye contains a vitreous fluid that is used in traditional Frigostian recipes, when it replaces vinegar - but only if you let the eye ferment for long enough.",ep:0,g:592,l:65,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11256] = {n:"Gullipop Beak",t:47,d:"Gullipops are rather stupid, badly behaved creatures, whose guano lies scattered in stinking piles around the port of Frigost. They like to steal fish from fishermen, but once well-trained, they are able to \"liberate\" the personal effects of distracted tourists and hide them in their beaks.",ep:0,g:667,l:75,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11257] = {n:"Gullipop Feather",t:53,d:"Frigostian schoolchildren use these feathers to write with, which is why mother Gullipops always stress the need to accelerate when passing a school to their chicks.",ep:0,g:648,l:75,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,an:0,p:10};
I.u[11258] = {n:"Chief Anbifketf\'s Receipt",t:24,d:"The date the pines were received is marked on this receipt. Show it to Gormor the Mangler to receive your pay.",ep:0,g:26,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11259] = {n:"Pine Trunks",t:24,d:"Chief Anbifketf needs these trunks for the pipework heating system.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11260] = {n:"Pingwin Blubber",t:24,d:"This thick and sticky blubber makes an excellent fuel that burns for a long, long time - which explains why Pengwins never feel the cold.",ep:0,g:500,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11261] = {n:"Damar\'s List of Supplies",t:24,d:"This list shows the missing pieces the fishermen of the Frozen Lake need to repair their equipment.",ep:0,g:41,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11262] = {n:"Damar\'s Wedding Ring",t:24,d:"Damar gave this ring to Valy Domidat thirty years ago.",ep:0,g:27,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11263] = {n:"Izterik Fairywork",t:74,d:"This fairywork produces a pleasant pyrotechnic effect for a few seconds and burns your retinas for the rest of your life.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:1,ut:true,p:1};
I.u[11264] = {n:"Shredded Pingwin Skin",t:24,d:"This Pingwin skin is in very poor condition. You won\'t be able to use it to make new underwear for Captain Chafer Day.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11265] = {n:"Domesticated Pingwobble",t:32,d:"This Pingwobble has been trained to be able to regurgitate enormous quantities of Icefish and leave them intact. The only problem is, its digestive process starts after half an hour.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,an:0,m:true,p:1};
I.u[11266] = {n:"Domesticated Pingwobble Brain",t:24,d:"While you were fighting, your Pingwobble was eaten. This is all that\'s left of him.",ep:0,g:89,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11267] = {n:"Discount",t:24,d:"This discount will be apply when you rent a room in the upcoming ice hotel.",ep:0,g:72,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,p:1};
I.u[11268] = {n:"Old Feca Plush",t:24,d:"This old plush has to belong to someone, but who?\nDouble-click to use.",ep:0,g:680,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,c:"Qc=599",u:true,p:1};
I.u[11269] = {n:"Chewing Gum",t:24,d:"The gum is of no use to you because your breath is too bad. On the other hand, Mac Gayver, the Xelor, will find a surprising use for it.",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,c:"Qc=600",u:true,p:1};
I.u[11270] = {n:"Family Chest",t:24,d:"This chest contains many heirlooms. In the absence of anyone else, you might be able to claim a reward from its owner.\nDouble-click to use.",ep:0,g:44,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,c:"Qc=601",u:true,p:1};
I.u[11271] = {n:"Sealed Book",t:24,d:"This sealed book is in poor condition. Forcing it open to read its contents may make it unusable. You\'d better hire a professional, but which one?\nDouble-click to use.",ep:0,g:95,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,c:"Qc=602",u:true,p:1};
I.u[11272] = {n:"",t:24,d:"",ep:0,g:0,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,c:"Qc=603",u:true,p:1};
